Regulation (EEC) No 3030/93 is amended as follows:
1. in Annex II the words 'United Arab Emirates` are inserted after 'Ukraine`;
2. in Article 28 (6), first indent, of Annex III the words 'United Arab Emirates = AE` are inserted after 'Ukraine = UA`;
3. in Table A of Annex III the table appearing in Annex I to this Regulation is inserted after the table applicable for Turkmenistan;
4. in the table to Annex VIII the table appearing in Annex II to this Regulation is inserted after the table applicable for Turkmenistan;
5. in Annex XI the words 'United Arab Emirates` are inserted after 'Uganda`.
